":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T00:05:39.000Z","msg":"買season pass仲多兩隻重製game<br />\n賓妹幾好玩"},{"pid":"1dfc34a825b086f024888f6a0571e0e457be61f5","tid":2114241,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T00:14:02.000Z","msg":"劇情黎講兩隻都OK....<br />\n玩法其實又咩大分別.....<br />\n同埋多左幾招新技能...<br />\n最麻煩係傭兵排行榜啲敵人難殺左好多....."},{"pid":"0bd0e5427e78aecbf21904efb3f98ab076ed716a","tid":2114241,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"䄂劍都ok，講主角成家立室"},{"pid":"9a44dc36df65c0fb03a9b0da5f7e077de8513a4c","tid":2114241,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"已買SEASON PASS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無話要玩邊隻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b2bf765c647b686c021fdc61ca7fb93508516c","tid":2114241,"uid":43114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a44dc36df65c0fb03a9b0da5f7e077de8513a4c","tid":2114241,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"已買SEASON PASS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無話要玩邊隻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T00:34:41.000Z","msg":"賓妹"},{"pid":"c2b5b275a37f76f8ec7ce241940f8e74aacc8bfc","tid":2114241,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a44dc36df65c0fb03a9b0da5f7e077de8513a4c","tid":2114241,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"已買SEASON PASS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無話要玩邊隻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T00:36:33.000Z","msg":"故事嚟講就袖劍先，亞特蘭提斯後<br />\n亞特蘭提斯敵人難打啲，可以練高級先去<br />\n唔跟故事玩就冇咩所謂"},{"pid":"fc6b49b3266ee35061e75e5700cceba4c96b5fd2","tid":2114241,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dis